        Setup an auto-collider system for a given physical model.
        Parameters:
        mdl - the model.
        size - the size of individual voxels
        nbX - voxels along X dimension
        nbY - voxels along Y dimension
        nbZ - voxels along Z dimension
        K - stiffness of autocollision interactions
        Z - damping of autocollision interactions
